title: Spin the Wheel: Loser Has To Wear A Cat Tail + Why Lunchbox Pretended to Be Raymundo’s Dad + Laci Kaye Booth on the Most Nerve Racking part of American Idol
itunes:title: Spin the Wheel: Loser Has To Wear A Cat Tail + Why Lunchbox Pretended to Be Raymundo’s Dad + Laci Kaye Booth on the Most Nerve Racking part of American Idol
description:
We spin the wheel and loser has to wear a cat tail. Bases on a story about a school having a problem with students dressing as cats and hissing at people. In “Pick A Bit” we hear about why Lunchbox went out to a construction site to post as Raymundo’s dad. We talk to Laci Kaye Booth about her time on American Idol, her new single and how she got a blue check mark on Instagram.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
